@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<h2>@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
<strong>@Model.Message</strong>

<p>
    This application is composed of the following modules:
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li><strong>TodoWeb:</strong> this an ASP.NET Core Razor Pages application</li>
        <li><strong>TodoApi:</strong> this an ASP.NET Core Web API application</li>
    </ul>
    The <strong>TodoWeb</strong> web application invokes the REST service exposed by <strong>TodoApi</strong> web application.
    <br />Both applications were built in C# using .NET standard and run inside separate Docker containers.
</p>
